thread.title: Thommy Konsta
thread.title_full: Jonny Sound & Video reviewed by Thommy Konsta

author: Thommy Konsta
title: Thommy Konsta
text: Johnny's professional and expert media knowledge is AMAZING! He created a video for my business which I use for advertising purposes (Kickboxing School) and over 3 months I have gotten over 10,000 views. I can't thank him enough! It has brought so much business to my door step. Highly recommended!
